hits.definition:
专 (F 專, 耑)

[zhuān] (= 专门 zhuānmén) special, (= 专家 zhuānjiā) expert;

    专政 zhuānzhèng dictatorship

若

[ruò] seem, as if;

    假若 jiǎruò if;

    若干 ruògān how much?

[rě] 般若 bōrě buddhist widom, prajna

兵

[bīng] (= 士兵 shìbīng) soldier;

    兵力 bīnglì military strength

{Compare with 宾 bīn guest}

志

[zhì] (= 意志 yìzhì) will, (= 标志 biāozhì) mark;

同志 tóngzhì comrade, (F 誌) 杂志 zázhì magazine

飞 (F 飛)

[fēi] fly;

    飞机 fēijī airplane

争 (F 爭)

[zhēng] contend, dispute;

    战争 zhànzhēng war, warfare;

    斗争 dòuzhēng fight, struggle

组 (F 組)

[zǔ] organize, group;

    组织 zǔzhī organization, organize, form

喜

[xǐ] happiness;

    喜欢 xǐhuān like
